All right.

1441
01:02:00,116 --> 01:02:03,152
Chef Sung-jun,
how determined are you for this round?

1442
01:02:03,219 --> 01:02:06,022
Chef Nam-no and I formed a team.

1443
01:02:06,089 --> 01:02:08,224
-I see.
-What's the team called?

1444
01:02:08,291 --> 01:02:10,093
Chef Anti-Good Vibes.

1445
01:02:10,159 --> 01:02:12,628
-Anti-good vibes?
-Anti-good vibes?

1446
01:02:12,695 --> 01:02:14,831
Good cooks
aren't supposed to be good-looking.

1447
01:02:16,132 --> 01:02:17,567
It adds more charm.

1448
01:02:17,633 --> 01:02:20,536
-No.
-We cannot condone that.

1449
01:02:20,603 --> 01:02:23,106
-We formed this union last week.
-I see.

1450
01:02:23,172 --> 01:02:24,774
We must win against Chef Jong-won.

1451
01:02:24,841 --> 01:02:28,611
Nam-no and Sung-jun,
do you like Chef Kang-rok?

1452
01:02:29,178 --> 01:02:30,446
We love him.

1453
01:02:31,881 --> 01:02:34,083
Kang-rok doesn't seem too pleased.

1454
01:02:34,150 --> 01:02:37,053
-He isn't even smiling.
-He doesn't look happy.

1455
01:02:37,120 --> 01:02:40,723
It's because of your cap.
This will change when you take it off.

1456
01:02:41,324 --> 01:02:44,360
-He has good-looking features.
-He does.

1457
01:02:44,427 --> 01:02:48,865
Chef Sohyi, do chefs in Austria
care about their looks and style?

1458
01:02:48,931 --> 01:02:51,534
I only hire handsome chefs.

1459
01:02:51,601 --> 01:02:53,069
-I see.
-See?

1460
01:02:53,136 --> 01:02:55,438
I mean, I have an open kitchen.

1461
01:02:55,505 --> 01:02:58,741
If you had to take one to Austria,
who would you take?

1462
01:02:59,609 --> 01:03:00,977
Why do you ask?

1463
01:03:01,043 --> 01:03:02,178
We're just curious.

1464
01:03:02,245 --> 01:03:04,747
Why? You can already tell.

1465
01:03:04,814 --> 01:03:06,883
-Yes.
-She's so candid.

1466
01:03:06,949 --> 01:03:08,985
Again, she has an open kitchen.

1467
01:03:09,051 --> 01:03:10,987
-He has an open kitchen too.
-Mine is open too.

1468
01:03:11,053 --> 01:03:12,989
We have open kitchens too.

1469
01:03:13,055 --> 01:03:16,859
The theme of your round is dessert.

1470
01:03:16,926 --> 01:03:18,294
Chef Sung-jun put up a wonderful fight

1471
01:03:18,361 --> 01:03:20,196
