reached three million.

1474
01:03:26,669 --> 01:03:28,204
-That's a fact.
-That's a fact.

1475
01:03:28,271 --> 01:03:30,306
-It means he proved himself.
-Yes.

1476
01:03:30,373 --> 01:03:32,341
Among Korean fine dining chefs,

1477
01:03:32,408 --> 01:03:36,179
Son Jong-won is said to have had
the most desserts. Is this true?

1478
01:03:36,245 --> 01:03:37,580
I actually love desserts,

1479
01:03:37,647 --> 01:03:39,549
