1480
01:03:41,083 --> 01:03:43,986
It means my dessert staff
always has a tough time,

1481
01:03:44,053 --> 01:03:46,722
<i>but if you look at the result,</i>
<i>it always looks great.</i>

1482
01:03:46,789 --> 01:03:47,890
-<i>I see.</i>
-<i>You're serious.</i>

1483
01:03:47,957 --> 01:03:50,193
It's also because we just had skate.

1484
01:03:50,259 --> 01:03:52,995
Right? Aren't you craving dessert?

1485
01:03:53,062 --> 01:03:56,432
-I can still smell it in my nose.
-It's strong.

1486
01:03:56,499 --> 01:03:59,168
It's still lingering.

1487
01:03:59,235 --> 01:04:00,236
CHEF SUNG-JUN'S INGREDIENTS:

1488
01:04:00,303 --> 01:04:01,304
MACADAMIA ICE CREAM,
CHOCOLATE JAM

1489
01:04:01,370 --> 01:04:02,371
ESPRESSO, CINNAMON CEREAL,
COCONUT MILK,

1490
01:04:02,438 --> 01:04:03,739
CHOCOLATE COOKIE,
GREEK YOGURT, AND MORE

1491
01:04:03,806 --> 01:04:05,474
Here's the dish I prepared today.

1492
01:04:07,410 --> 01:04:11,013
TIRAMISU AGAIN

1493
