-Heuksando is famous for skate, right?
-Yes.

1501
01:04:30,399 --> 01:04:34,136
Veneto is where tiramisu originated from.

1502
01:04:34,203 --> 01:04:38,174
I learned it while working
at a three-star Michelin restaurant there.

1503
01:04:39,075 --> 01:04:41,110
I learned the authentic recipe.

1504
01:04:41,177 --> 01:04:43,212
Is it different?

1505
01:04:43,279 --> 01:04:44,480
It's a bit different.

1506
01:04:44,547 --> 01:04:47,350
How you use the eggs is
the most important.

1507
01:04:47,416 --> 01:04:52,121
Also, there's a cream cheese
called mascarpone,

1508
01:04:52,188 --> 01:04:53,723
but I won't use that today.

1509
01:04:54,257 --> 01:04:57,093
-I'll only make it with milk.
-Really?

1510
01:04:57,159 --> 01:04:58,294
-Whoa.
-Can he do that?

1511
01:04:58,361 --> 01:05:01,564
I'll serve that with yogurt
similar to lassi,

1512
01:05:01,631 --> 01:05:03,900
made with coconut milk and mango

1513
01:05:03,966 --> 01:05:06,702
to add a nice, refreshing touch.

1514
01:05:07,136 --> 01:05:10,306
CHEF JONG-WON'S INGREDIENTS:
MASCARPONE CHEESE, ESPRESSO

1515
01:05:10,373 --> 01:05:11,741
VANILLA COFFEE,
CHOCOLATE COOKIE,

1516
01:05:11,807 --> 01:05:13,542
CHOCOLATE SNACK,
CHOCOLATE BAR, CHOCOLATE

