1521
01:05:23,552 --> 01:05:26,322
-I prepared Tirami-Chelin.
-Tirami-Chelin.

1522
01:05:26,389 --> 01:05:28,925
Do that for us. "Tirami-Chelin." Do it.

1523
01:05:28,991 --> 01:05:30,459
-Tirami-Chelin.
-Do it!

1524
01:05:30,526 --> 01:05:32,395
-Tirami-Chelin.
-Come on!

1525
