Chef Sung-jun is doing something else.

1616
01:09:13,349 --> 01:09:17,119
He needs that soft cream to make tiramisu.

1617
01:09:17,186 --> 01:09:19,955
That's what he'll make
by clotting milk with lemon juice.

1618
