1651
01:10:45,474 --> 01:10:47,810
-This time, it's green.
-Yes.

1652
01:10:47,876 --> 01:10:49,478
Mr. Balloon.

1653
01:10:49,545 --> 01:10:51,080
MR. BALLOON WITH GOOD VIBES

1654
01:10:51,146 --> 01:10:53,782
-He's Mr. Balloon.
-You can put some water inside

1655
01:10:53,849 --> 01:10:57,686
