It'll stand back up like a roly-poly.

1656
01:10:58,587 --> 01:11:00,055
I would've done that.

1657
01:11:00,723 --> 01:11:03,359
-Chef Hyun-suk would've done that.
-Right?

1658
01:11:03,425 --> 01:11:05,861
-Jong-won has a long way to go.
-No.

1659
01:11:05,928 --> 01:11:09,031
He needs to learn some more.

1660
01:11:09,098 --> 01:11:10,299
Stop it.

1661
